Double-boiled Papaya Milk Peach Gum 木瓜牛奶炖桃胶 with Similac Mum is a nourishing dessert for women, especially for mums on confinement and breastfeeding mums.
.

Similac Mum is a maternal milk for pregnant and breastfeeding mums. It is suitable for weight management during pregnancy and breastfeeding and provides a host of valuable nutrients with less fat. Similac Mum is the most complete* maternal milk with 27 essential vitamins and minerals, and prebiotic (FOS), assisting mums to meet their increased nutritional needs during pregnancy and breastfeeding.
.

Do stay tuned for my next post where I’ll be sharing the recipe.
. *Comparison among all maternal milk in Singapore as of January 2020 both per 100 g of powder and per serving.
.
